Everyone, Kon-muscle~! From Hololive 3rd generation, the... muscle-brain! Shirogane Noel here!

503
00:37:15,605 --> 00:37:18,605
はーいこんやっぴー！ホロライブ4期生の常闇トワ様でーす！
Hi, Kon-yappi! It's Hololive 4th generation's Tokoyami Towa-sama!

504
00:37:19,105 --> 00:37:20,605
本物だ！もうこんな感じです...
