505
00:37:22,105 --> 00:37:29,105
こんねね～ ホロライブ5期生 トワ様とラブラブな桃鈴ねねでーす！
Kon-nene~! Hololive 5th generation, the one who's lovey-dovey with Towa-sama, Momosuzu Nene!

506
00:37:30,105 --> 00:37:37,105
